cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper focuses on the task of Visual Dialogue, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel model for deep visual understanding, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also uses a feature selection framework, which could be related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
